original: Larsson, Inge John Axel, andre läkare, Vadstena, f. 28/12/09 i Visby av sjökapt. lohn L. o. Lillie Hellström. G. 40 m. Gulli Blomberg. Barn: Ulf 1. 43. — Stud:ex. i Visby 29, med. kand. i Lund 33 o. med. lic. där 38. E. läk. v. Vipeholms sjukh. o. Tyringe sanat. 37, v. S:t Lars sjukh. 38, e. o. andre läk. där 39, andre läk. v. Birgittas sjukh. i Vadstena sed. 43.
translated: Larsson, Inge John Axel, second physician, Vadstena, b. 28/12/09 in Visby to Captain John L. and Lillie Hellström. Married in 1940 to Gulli Blomberg. Children: Ulf, born in 1943. Completed high school in Visby in 1929, obtained a bachelor's degree in medicine in Lund in 1933, and a medical license there in 1938. Worked as an assistant physician at Vipeholm Hospital and Tyringe Sanatorium in 1937, at S:t Lars Hospital in 1938, as a temporary second physician there in 1939, and as a second physician at Birgitta's Hospital in Vadstena since 1943.
